{\rtf1\ansi \deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fswiss .VnArial;}}{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red255\green255\blue255;\red0\green0\blue0;\red0\green128\blue0;}\deftab720\plain \f0 \fs28 \b \cf1 \pard\qc \sb100 \sa100 \sl280 Ngh\'d6 thu\'cbt l\'b5m \'ae\'d1p\plain \f0 \fs24  \par \plain \f0 \fs36 \b \cf4 10 \'aei\'d2u c\'c7n ch\'f3 \'fd khi g\'e9i \'ae\'c7u v\'b5 s\'b6 t\'e3c\plain \f0 \fs24  \par \plain \f0 \fs26 \pard\qj \li288 \ri288 \sb144 \sl260 1. Kh\'abng n\'aan g\'e9i \'ae\'c7u b\'bbng d\'c7u h\'b5ng ng\'b5y, d\'efng d\'c7u g\'e9i li\'aan t\'f4c m\'e7i ng\'b5y ho\'b5n to\'b5n kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 \'aei\'d2u t\'e8t cho t\'e3c b\'b9n. \par 2. Khi g\'e9i h\'b7y s\'f6 d\'f4ng d\'c7u g\'e9i 2 l\'c7n. L\'c7n th\'f8 nh\'cat \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m s\'b9ch b\'f4i, b\'c8n v\'b5 d\'c7u.L\'c7n th\'f8 2 l\'b5m s\'b9ch s\'a9u v\'b5 k\'fc l\'ad\'ecng h\'acn, sau \'ae\'e3 g\'e9i l\'b9i t\'e3c nhi\'d2u l\'c7n b\'bbng n\'ad\'edc s\'b9ch. \par 3. N\'d5u t\'e3c b\'b9n tr\'eb l\'aan s\'ac v\'b5 r\'f4ng, h\'b7y v\'b5o si\'aau th\'de t\'d7m lo\'b9i d\'c7u g\'e9i c\'f9c s\'b9ch (deep -cleaning) Sau khi s\'f6 d\'f4ng lo\'b9i d\'c7u n\'b5y ch\'f5ng m\'e9t tu\'c7n b\'b9n c\'e3 th\'d3 y\'aan t\'a9m quay l\'b9i v\'edi d\'a9\'ef g\'e9i \'ae\'c7u c\'f2. \par 4. N\'d5u b\'b9n c\'e3 m\'b8i t\'e3c d\'b5i, th\'d7 khi g\'e9i nh\'ed b\'bet \'ae\'c7u t\'f5 trong ra ngo\'b5i \'ae\'d3 c\'e3 th\'d3 l\'b5m s\'b9ch \'ae\'ad\'eec to\'b5n b\'e9 m\'b8i t\'e3c. \tab \par \plain \f0 \fs26 \cf1 </TBODY>\plain \f0 \fs26 \tab \par 5. Khi g\'e9i \'ae\'c7u b\'b9n n\'aan d\'efng n\'ad\'edc \'cam nh\'adng l\'c7n tr\'b8ng cu\'e8i c\'efng n\'aan d\'efng n\'ad\'edc l\'b9nh ho\'c6c n\'ad\'edc m\'b8t. N\'ad\'edc m\'b8t s\'cf l\'b5m cho t\'e3c b\'b9n \'ae\'d1p h\'acn. \par 6. Kh\'abng n\'aan l\'b9m d\'f4ng d\'c7u g\'e9i \'ae\'c7u. Qu\'b8 nhi\'d2u b\'e4t x\'b5 ph\'dfng ch\'bcng \'aeem l\'b9i \'aei\'d2u g\'d7 t\'e8t m\'b5 c\'dfn c\'e3 h\'b9i cho t\'e3c. H\'acn n\'f7a sau khi g\'e9i xong c\'f2ng kh\'abng n\'aan lau t\'e3c qu\'b8 m\'b9nh ch\'d8 v\'d7 mu\'e8n t\'e3c kh\'ab nhanh. \par 7. Nh\'f7ng lo\'b9i d\'c7u c\'e3 h\'ad\'acng v\'de tr\'b8i c\'a9y v\'b5 h\'ad\'acng hoa thi\'aan nhi\'aan nh\'ad hoa hu\'d6, hoa b\'ad\'ebi... s\'cf \'aeem l\'b9i chob\'b9n c\'b6m gi\'b8c d\'d4 ch\'deu h\'acn nh\'f7ng h\'ad\'acng th\'acm ki\'d3u ho\'b8 ch\'cat t\'e6ng h\'eep. \par 8. N\'d5u t\'e3c b\'b9n qu\'b8 x\'ac h\'b7y d\'f5ng vi\'d6c d\'efng d\'c7u g\'e9i c\'e3 c\'b6 ch\'cat s\'b6 t\'e3c b\'ebi ch\'cat n\'b5y l\'b5m t\'e3c b\'b9n n\'c6ng th\'aam. B\'b9n n\'aan th\'f6 d\'efng ch\'f5ng hai gi\'e4t silicon pha v\'edi d\'c7u g\'e9i trong l\'dfng b\'b5n tay, Th\'f8 h\'e7n h\'eep n\'b5y khi g\'e9i s\'cf kh\'abng l\'b5m n\'c6ng v\'b5 x\'ac t\'e3c b\'b9n \'ae\'a9u. \par 9.Trong m\'e4i tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep kh\'abng n\'aan l\'b9m d\'f4ng d\'c7u x\'b6 t\'e3c. N\'d5u b\'b9n d\'efng lo\'b9i d\'c7u g\'e9i v\'b5 x\'b6 ri\'aang th\'d7 n\'aan b\'abi ch\'cat x\'b6 t\'e3c v\'b5o v\'efng ch\'a9n t\'e3c b\'de kh\'ab v\'b5 ch\'b6i b\'bbng l\'ad\'eec c\'e3 r\'a8ng to. N\'d5u nh\'ad t\'e3c b\'b9n ti\'d5t ra d\'c7u t\'f9 nhi\'aan b\'b9n c\'e3 th\'d3 kh\'abng c\'c7n ch\'a8m ch\'f3t ch\'a9n t\'e3c. \par \pard\qj \li288 \ri288 \sb144 \sl260 \tx1134 \tx2268 \tx3402 \tx4536 \tx5670 \tx6804 \tx7938 \tx9072 \tx10206 \tx11340 \tx12474 \tx13608 \tx14742 \tx15876 10. Lau t\'e3c nh\'d1 nh\'b5ng b\'bbng kh\'a8n v\'b5 sau \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'d3 t\'e3c t\'f9 kh\'ab. Kh\'abng n\'aan ch\'b6i t\'e3c khi t\'e3c c\'dfn \'ad\'edt.}